<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=7860&amp;p=79797#p79797"><![CDATA[
"Nintendo convention" is the convention used by most hardware since it allows the line/vertical counter to be used directly for background rendering and sprite Y comparisons.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=20">kyuusaku</a> — Tue Jun 14, 2011 2:00 pm</p><hr />
